#### Upload Configurations
- Maximum file size: 5MB
- Allowed image types: jpg, png, gif
- Secure filename generation using UUID
- Separate directories by content type

### Testing Structure

```
tests/
├── conftest.py           # Shared fixtures
├── api/                  # API endpoint tests
│   └── v1/
